# UI Design Rules (Tody-like minimal, soft cards, hand-drawn icons)

## Design Goal
Build a calm, minimalist PWA UI with:
- soft card surfaces
- lots of whitespace
- rounded corners
- subtle shadows
- gentle status indicators (dots + small chips)
- friendly hand-drawn/monoline illustrations

Do NOT add gamification, bright gradients, heavy borders, or dense dashboards.

