## Color + Surface Tokens
Use a warm off-white background and subtle pastel surfaces.

### Base
- App background: off-white / paper (#F6F3EF-ish)
- Card background: white (#FFFFFF)
- Divider lines: very light gray (#E9E4DD-ish)

### Pastels (only for tile backgrounds / small accents)
- Mint / soft green
- Powder blue
- Warm beige / sand
- Soft rose (only for overdue chip)

Rules:
- Never use saturated colors.
- Do not use gradients.
- Pastels appear as very light background tints only.

