## Icons & Illustrations
Important: Use TWO icon styles:
1) Functional UI icons (gear, plus, nav icons): monoline icon set (e.g., Lucide).
2) Area illustrations (kitchen pot, bathtub, sofa, clipboard) + house mood: hand-drawn SVGs.

Rules:
- UI icons: stroke only, rounded caps, consistent size (20‚Äì24px).
- Illustrations: simple black/gray linework + tiny pastel fill + minimal shadow.
- No detailed drawings, no photorealism.

Implementation guidance:
- Create an <Illustration name="kitchen" /> component that renders a local SVG.
- Create a <IconButton> component for consistent gear/plus buttons.

